title: A Prince Of A Guy
description:
Description :
        Sean had to take care of his niece for just two weeks, but the mischievous angel drove him crazy all day long, and he couldn’t focus on his work! So he decided to place an ad for a babysitter in the local newspaper. The only applicant was an unassuming, frumpy-looking woman. But looks didn’t matter as long as she could save him from his situation! Little did he know that Carlyne was a Russian princess! She just wanted to live an ordinary life for once and escape her life in the public eye.
